\f1 \

\f0  Context                                                                  
\f1 \

\f0                                                                                                           
\f1 \

\f0  The MSC Cargo Brand Manager Genie Space is deployed with 12 tables (4 dimensions + 8 facts) on
\f1 \

\f0  \cf4 fevm-serverless-stable-3n0ihb.cloud.databricks.com\cf2 . The brand manager needs a single-pane-of-glass app that combines KPI
\f1 \

\f0  monitoring, AI-powered analytics (via Genie), email composition, and campaign planning. The APX framework (FastAPI + React) is
\f1 \

\f0   chosen to enable future extensions with Agent SDK, MCP server capabilities, and Lakebase backend.
\f1 \
